  //    1. Transactional: Sex workers, explicit arrangements. Bond irrelevant.
  //    2. Hedonist: Hedonist/casual NPCs may have lower barrier (Bond 4 + explicit invitation).
  //    3. Exploitation: Vulnerability/desperation (dark tone). Bond secondary.
